ht dance on her glistening trim body!<br>He smiles gently, remembering a moment is his time of a vision such as this!!<br>Watches as she lays a snowy-white towel to opalized hair - shaking &amp; teasing its long length to dry near her fire!<br><br>Pushing himself away, he leaves as quietly as he had come. He came to see this vision of loveliness by accident--he feels no shame! What his age-old eyes beheld, will be treasured in his heart, till his passing - to once again unite with the wife he still loves!!<br><br>****Enfolding Night-Black silk to fragrant skin, ties the sash!<br>Chaz'et's mind at peace, sits to the Brown-stoned hearth. Violet eyes look to - crackling orange flames - her mind journeys, seeking her pet of bone.<br>Hearing his Mistress call, quickly finishes his task given him. Gathering these strange, deadly plants he has located in the sewers of &quot;Qeynos Underground&quot;, departs to return to her. <br><br>Success in finding her pet, Chaz'et prepares for: what will be-most deadly to both her &amp; Darrien - if anything goes wrong in her preparations of the plants!!<br>&quot;Nasty Business is about with those scum of Qeynos Tunnels!!&quot; &quot;Let us see if, per-chance--&quot;I&quot; am NOT more deadly that they!!&quot; <br><br>As Darrien moans, Chaz'et feels of his forehead. &quot;SHADES!!&quot; &quot;I must lower his fever!!&quot; &quot;He is burning UP!!&quot;<br>Placing a basin of cold spring-water near, begins to undress this man. Layer upon layer, she removes. Hand trembling - steals herself against her desires of this Ranger!! Praying her heart will with-stand the onslaught!!<br>Cooling waters begin their soothing of his poisoned mind &amp; body.<br><br>***Darrien's mind is adrift on Hell's Winged Minions! Mild shock runs through his body, as a coolness descends on his fevered thoughts! &quot;I am lost!!&quot; &quot;Why can NOT I awake this nightmare I live??&quot;<br>Three words escapes his tortured lips: &quot;Azzarria!&quot; &quot;My beloved!&quot;<br><br>***A nasty frown crosses this Necromancer's brow!!! &quot;Nay - Nay!!&quot; Who is this AZZARRIA??!!&quot; &quot;I will 'FIND' this woman OUT!!&quot; &quot;WHO is SHE to Darrien??!&quot;<br>Unbridled anger drives a wedge sharply near her heart for this female!!<br>&quot;Think NO MORE of this now!&quot; &quot;You have work to do!!&quot; Drawing deeply a pain-wracked breath, continues her cooling of Darrien.<br><br>As long moments travel - snail-paced! Chaz'et sees the beginning of his fevered-flush leave him. Finding a gossamar sheet, lays it gently over him to protect him from a chill.<br>Running aching fingers of desire through his thick dark hair, places a lingering Kiss to his now cool brow.<br><br>A shimmer appears to her left, bringing her pet of bone back to her side.<br>Arthritic claws of white-bleached bone, release their guarded possession to the wooden table before her.<br>&quot;AH!&quot; &quot;Aye!&quot; &quot;You have done well my pet, in the gathering of these vile plants!&quot; <br>Reaching - brushes his skull with the back of her soft hand in gratitude before sending him back to his plane of Unrest.<br><br>Before her lies:<br>Hellsbane<br>Rythap<br>Ot'Wart<br>Three of the most deadly plants known to this world! If brewed correctly..these three will enhance great power to whomever drinks of this. If done wrong - Agonizing Death!!!<br><br>Grinding the Hellsband &amp; Rythap to fine powder, places in her pot upon the hearth. Palms sweaty - reaches for the Ot'wart, receiving a nasty sting to her finger! Even in its Death throes its vicious!!<br><br>As this is brewing, Chaz'et reaches inside her belt pouch pulling forth a &quot;Living Liquid&quot;, the color of Sun-Kissed straw. Looking at this, she has always been mesmerized - watching it swirl lazily within its glass prison! Pulling the glass stopper a single golden wisp slids out onto her up-turned palm. <br>What she now holds will be her balance to the deadly brew she must consume!<br>Adding the golden wisp to the strained plant brew - Drinks of it quickly, before losing her nerve!!<br><br>**The time is Nigh!!<br>Standing stock-still, Chaz'et is terrified of what will become OR- rather what this poison will do inside her!! Once only had she heard in long-ago tales, of One who tried this. Alas!! It was in vain! His Death:<br>Appalling!!<br><br>**The Beginning**<br>Light-headedness creeps &amp; crawls within her mind - seeking to rip her minds boundries &amp; escape its confinement! Heavyness of limb - breathe shallowed - her beating heart lurches, almost stopping its rhythm of life!!<br><br>SUDDENLY...Chaz'et experiences 'Insane' - 'Undeniable' power!! Expanding with-in every cell of her being!!! Her &quot;Dark-Side&quot; Reborn!!<br>&quot;My GODS!!&quot; &quot;Help ME!!&quot; &quot;It is over-powering my will!!!&quot; &quot;Seducing me, like a Sirens haunting call of ships &amp; Men!!!&quot;<br>Ornate Dark Power awakens!! Bending her mind to its own! Growing! Feeding voraciously on her soul evil-born!!!!<br><br>The once cozy room expands with insidious levity! Earth-shuddering Lightening traces patterns near her - THEN striking her full ON!! Bizarre winds pelt her!!!<br><br>Chaz'ets eyes take on a glow of eerie extraneus light!! Her long silvered-hair flowing wild &amp; unbidden - filling the room with its Jasmine-scented splendor!!<br>&quot;SHE&quot; is still within, but barely!! A name is whispered on those rubied-lips: &quot;Darriennn&quot;. Her longing desire of him is what NOW saves her sanity from this potion she has created and consumed!!!<br>Her body is surrounded by Azure light of un-natural essence! Over flowing with exquisite strength &amp; power!! It-radiating outwards encompassing her!!<br><br>Lifting Darrien to her breast - holds him to her!!<br><br>Poisoned enhanced magik bends to her command - encysting its azure aura around him! Darrien struggles-his screams, tearing the night--ripping her heart in two!!<br>Chaz'ets honeyed breath to his ear: &quot;Be still! - Please my Love!&quot; &quot;The magik is almost completed!!&quot;<br><br>Lifetimes seem to pass before her as she waits... THEN! The spell releases its grasp of him!<br><br>Shaken, she lays Darrien back to the softness of their bed, seeing a single tear drift to the pillow.<br><br>His breathing has slowed-the fever is GONE!! <br>Exhilaration surrounds her!! &quot;I&quot; have succeeded where 'ONE' other had failed!!!<br>Beside herself with joy, hugs Darrien, kissing him!!<br><br>~~~~The 'KISS' is returned with PASSION!!~~~~<br><br>Amazement strikes this Necromancer, but is quickly forgotten, as Darrien rolls to her - burying his hands into her rich heavy hair! Possesses her with unbridled abandon!!<br><br>**Dancing Orange-hued Firelight watches! - Beginning its sensous symphony of shadow-play over this couple!**<br><br>Fighting back from &quot;Deaths&quot; opened Door, Darrien knows NOT whom he's with!!!<br>OR-Does HE?!?<br><br>Part 15...To Be Continued<br>***Dedicated To A Very Special Druid in &quot;My Life&quot;!!<br><br>&quot;Stormchild&quot;<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br>Azzarria - "Stormchild"<br>"The Huntress"</td></tr>
