orces himself to do so!<br>Watching her as she attempts to brush Karana's earth from her lithe body, is forced to endure this intimate display! &quot;NAY!!!&quot; &quot;I can NOT stand this any longer!!!&quot;<br>Turns, walking back to the fire.<br><br><br>&quot;YES, WELL!&quot; - &quot;While you TWO were besting each other!&quot; - &quot;I&quot; laid a fresh fire &amp; started our breakfast!&quot;<br><br>Mid-brushing of her night apparel - Stops!<br>&quot;Brylin??&quot; &quot;Turn to Me!&quot;<br>Closing his eyes, knows what enticing beauty awaits them--turns back to her.<br><br>Clear blue eyes access him, traveling slowly - the entire length of him.<br>A puzzled frown crosses &amp; vanishes in a split second from her face! &quot;You - are looking extremely FIT this morning!!&quot;<br><br>&quot;AYE, Azzarria!&quot;<br>&quot;I&quot; feel a &quot;Changed&quot; person!!&quot; &quot;For this - I believe I have YOU to Thank!?&quot;<br>Remembering the foul brew, shivers!!! -- {&quot;Is this really where my healing came from??&quot;, he ponders} <br><br>Tilting that Red-Amber'd head to the side, nods slightly with questioning eyes. &quot;I&quot; was taught the art of healing with given herbs...AYE.&quot; &quot;I&quot; must say though&quot; - &quot;I never knew them to be this powerful so soon, in their healing!!&quot; <br><br>&quot;AYE-Lady!!&quot; Tis seems they have made their mark on ME!!!&quot;<br><br>Ponpi' yips---breaking the pregnant silence that had fallen between them!! {Wisdom in this animal, not yet letting the two know of &quot;Possible&quot; horrors ahead for them---Letting their strenths and knowledge of each other be sealed!!}<br><br>Both laughing at once, head to their campfire. All three stomachs rumbling protests of neglect!<br><br>Finishing - a comfortable silence settles - as each looks to the other with growing interests.<br>**ONE interest in particular! - Erupting with desire, but tightly leashed for the moment!!!<br><br>