	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=189461><span id=Sage>Taimarawee</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>20 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>**Luclin's massive bulk hovers precariously in the Heavens, shining Winter bright to the landscape below**<br><br>***With cunning, known to her kind--she finds him!<br>The werewolves plaintive cries echo the cold dark night!!<br><br>Lowering her massive head, nuzzles once more her Mate!!!<br>Stiff, with death, the Male can not respond!<br><br>Biting at her ragged haunch, worries a flea to the surface, relieving the itch--Sits--to gather her young closer!<br>Leaning into their Mothers warmth, instinctively feeling her loss, makes the Kits edgy &amp; quarrelsome!!<br><br>Snappy at her un-ruly young-moves off from them, sitting once more!!<br><br>Blood-Red Eyes pierce the silent night! In the distance, she senses Another-YET-not quite, of her kind!<br>Scarred lips curl back, drawing across deadly sharp--yellowing teeth!! Snarling deep within her throat, calls to the &quot;OTHER!&quot; Unlike her distant cousins--who mate for life--it matters NOT to this One!!<br>Through no fault of her own, survival instinct drives her to pursue the &quot;One&quot; she is sensing!!!<br><br>Returning her kits to their hidden cave, once more returns to where she had been.<br><br>***No longer Human, NOR--Druid-Wolf--Unseeing eyes open--Of tinted red angry hue!!<br><br>Infected Wounds begin to Heal!! Ravaged flesh becoming whole!! Muscles tighten &amp; twist to bizarre formations!! Bones BREAK, re-shaping!!<br><br>Grinding &amp; Gnashing his teeth, against the gruesome transformation--Brylin is helpless to fight against it!!!<br><br>&quot;Werewolf&quot; contaminates within!!! Hungerily, consuming his pure-blood wolfen side!!<br>A low-gutteral sound erupts!!! Slashing, tearing, finally freeing the constrictive garments -- Stands upon heavily muscled legs, challenging the cold &quot;Moonlight&quot; washing over him!!!<br><br>Falling back to all fours - lopes away to a distant call!!<br><br>Ahead, Brylin - although - NO LONGER Brylin - Sees and Smells the female werewolf!<br>Gathering great speed, rushes her, knocking her to the ground, pinning her beneath his great bulk!!<br><br>Savage, feral urges over take him!! Mating has begun for this ungodly pair!!! Whom could stop this - NOR if seeing, would ever dare!!!<br><br>Deep within this altered Druid, revulsion fights to the surface! Unbound horror of what has taken place--screams for Brylin's human-side to fight back!!!<br><br>Warm memories of someone or something, jolt his altered mind!!! Biting deep to her neck, they hit a scree, tumbling as one to its bottom!!!<br>Putrid blood washing his thoat - gags releasing his hold of her!!<br><br>In blind panic the female twists free of Brylin!!<br>&quot;One&quot;--Pure Blood--&quot;One&quot; Tainted, face each other down!!!<br>The female sees inside those haunted eyes, a struggle for its release from this nightmare!!!<br><br>Dropping to the shaled earth beneath her, gives ground to this silvered male! Willing her bestial thoughts of her young to this un-nerving male - Is rewarded the release of him!!!<br><br>Crouching low, moves off carefully! Believing a safe distance now between them, looks back to Brylin. He has gone!<br>Fully straightening her wracked form, heads to her cave &amp; young...Never to call forth this ONE again!!<br><br>***As Luclin gives sway - Dawns rays break forth over the ridge.<br>&quot;Brylin&quot; returns, finding himself near a slow-moving river. Where be I?? Looking down, finds welts, scratch wounds &amp; NOTHING else!!!<br><br>Unclothed, filthy, confused, he dives into the river to soothe his hurts.<br><br>Clear memory will not surface this Druid!! Leaving the river, knows from distant memory, pain and near-death HAD been upon him!<br>&quot;How did I get HERE?&quot;<br>Seeing only pinkened--healed areas of skin, wonders: &quot;Where are the deep gashes, put upon me by that mangy werewolf??&quot; <br><br>One memory does come forth with clarity, stopping his ascent up the slippy bank!!!<br>Azzarria's touching of him--her soothing hands &amp; voice, instilling him to drink a potion of foul taste!!!<br><br>Catching himself, before that memory goes further -transfers to his wolfen-side!!<br>Being within this form, location no longer a mystery, pads back to her camp.<br>Approaching, finds her still to her bed, curled tight against Ponpi'. &quot;PONPI&quot;?? <br><br>Seeing her pet once more beside this lovely beastlord, shocks him--transfering Brylin back to his human form!!<br><br>Ponpi' hearing his approach, raises that proud Snow-White head. Eyes of great wisdom look to him, as if to say: &quot;Welcome back Druid&quot; - &quot;To the Land of the Living!&quot;<br><br>Shivering, with a sudden chill, builds up their fire, savoring its warmth.<br>Cramped muscles relax, Brylin feels better than he has felt in ages!!<br>Lying down on his blankets, lazy-sleep claims this changed man once more.<br><br>***&quot;What of the next rising of the &quot;Full-Moon&quot; Druid?&quot;<br>&quot;Will you remember nite last?&quot;<br>&quot;Is there now a new &quot;LIFE&quot; beginning in that Unholy Mating? <br>&quot;Pray Tell!!&quot; &quot;What will it be??&quot; &quot;Human?&quot; - &quot;Werewolf?&quot; - OR - something MUCH WORSE??!!&quot;<br><br>Part 13...To be continued<br></p>&nbsp;<br>Azzarria - "Stormchild"<br>"The Huntress"</td></tr>
