	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=189461><span id=Sage>Taimarawee</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>20 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>****Weak &amp; gasping from his arduous run, the messenger bursts forth into the &quot;Glade!&quot;<br>Skidding to a stop, tries to collect himself, but fails miserably!<br><br>&quot;Samuel!&quot; &quot;WHERE is Samuel??&quot;<br>Hearing his name echoing the village, Samuel answers: &quot;AH!&quot; &quot;Finally!!&quot; What have you learned of my son?!?&quot;<br><br>Words seem to constrict in the young mans throat--&quot;The news is grevious Sir!&quot; &quot;It appears, Darrien has killed a Cleric in Qeynos!!!&quot; &quot;The &quot;Bloodsabers&quot;, I am told have exacted revenge--hurting him severly!!&quot; BUT!!--Thinking their punishment too severe--after talking it over amoungst themselves--Went below to the Sewers to find and release him!&quot;<br>&quot;It seems--He has disappeared!!&quot; &quot;They can find NO Trace of HIM!!&quot;<br><br>Swaying..Samuel clutches his chest, whiteness beginning around his eyes and mouth--Shock has set in!! Terror for his only son, almost undoing his rational mind!!<br>&quot;SEWERS!!&quot; he yells. &quot;The filthy scum, put my Darrien in their Underground SEWERS!!&quot;<br><br>Drinel, hearing the strangeness creeping into Samuels voice, comes running to his aid--jus catching him as he collaspes!!<br>&quot;What is happening HERE??&quot; &quot;Never Mind&quot;--&quot;tell me, when we get Samuel to his bed!!&quot;<br>With the help of Laah, he is as settled as time will allow. Squeezing her hand for comfort, quickly gives his leave of her..to find the Elders for answers.<br><br>****Chaz'et paces back &amp; forth to the small room!!<br>&quot;Something is NOT right here!!&quot; &quot;This one should be healing faster!!&quot; Kneeling, once more to Darrien's side, grasps his wrist--finding a pulse point--it is very weak and thready!<br>&quot;There must be something else at play here, besides his physical injuries!!&quot;<br><br>Running her shakey fingers through now, lack-lustered hair, from not enough sleep &amp; worry, lets loose a low snarl of frustration!!<br><br>As Chaz'et kneels by this handsome Elf-Human, she smells something familiar on the air, emitting from those enticing lips of his! &quot;Those LIPS!!&quot;<br><br>**Forgotten--for the moment--is the odor!!!**<br><br>Leaning in, closer still--her silken tresses fall forward, trailing itself across Darrien's bare chest. Causing Darrien to moan in his delirium.--{What &quot;Vision&quot; does this bring up Ranger?}<br><br>Not being able to control her thoughts any more, Chaz'et's full-rubied lips seek &amp; conquer Darrien's!! Gently, gently opening his warmed mouth with her own, seeks the pleasures she has been thinking about since she saw him &amp; explores this wonder with unbidden pleasure!!<br><br>Darrien begins to respond to HER!!! Electric-shock pulsates on every nerve of her being!! Heavenly sensations like liquid-fire consume her!!<br><br>*&quot;A KNOCK&quot; on the splinter'd door, snaps her back from her Dream World!! A rosy-flush appears to her cheeks making her aware of how far that could of GONE!!!<br>&quot;SHADES!!&quot; Brushing off the dust from her midnight-blue gown--answers the knock.<br><br>Standing before her in the doorway is &quot;Zethe&quot; from the Tavern. Spicey-Pungent aroma from the food tray, making her mouth start to water!<br><br>&quot;OH!&quot; &quot;Yes-s!!&quot; I had forgotten I had ordered this!!&quot;<br>Sneaking a look around her, sees Darrien on the bed.<br>&quot;I&quot; understand M'Lady!!&quot;<br><br>A becoming blush rising to her cheeks--&quot;NO!&quot; &quot;You DO NOT UNDERSTAND SIR!!&quot; &quot;Please, if you will.&quot; &quot;Place the tray and leave US!&quot;<br><br>&quot;Yes, Mistress&quot;--Still smiling, takes his leave!<br><br>Sharply, Chaz'et turns to Darrien!!<br>&quot;A fool am I??&quot; &quot;I wonder??&quot; &quot;My mind is NOT my own as of Late!!&quot; Especially when I am near him!!&quot;<br><br>Remembering that vague familiar smell--quickly crosses the room.<br>Bending over &amp; breathing deeply of his breathe--stumbles back, nearly losing her footing!<br><br>&quot;POISON!!!&quot; &quot;This Ranger has been Poisoned!!!&quot;<br>&quot;Low-life-sneaky sewer scum!!!&quot; &quot;They will pay DEARLY for this!!&quot;<br><br>Calling forth her Pet-of-Bone, sends it on a urgent quest!<br><br>Macabre Lust for revenge lances through her heart at this injustice!!<br><br><br>****AH!! Young beautiful Necromancer with a Gentle Heart--Do you know what YOU DO??<br><br>A Blossom of Love has entered your Heart!! Something you have Guarded well these may years!!<br><br>Be Careful..Young One!! For this Man's Heart, may be hard to WIN!!!<br><br>****What Joys &amp; Sadness' are being planned for their futures???<br><br>&quot;Once again&quot;--Destiny &amp; Fate Are AT PLAY!!!<br><br>Part 12...To Be Continued<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br>Azzarria - "Stormchild"<br>"The Huntress"</td></tr>
