	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Wed, May 7th 7:11 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=189461><span id=Sage>Taimarawee</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>20 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>***Long Ago, I decided to see if I had any writing ability in me and this is what I FIRST wrote.<br>It was about my first character. An Erudite Enchantress.<br>***&quot;Mystiina&quot; was NOT Happy with her homes hunting grounds..So Ventured forth to Qeynos and the Hills...BE AWARE!! It is not that good, but from here on OUT, I found I was hooked and loved to write stories, be they good OR bad&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>***You Poor People...LOL!!!<br><br><br>****A Lesson Learned - &quot;TOO LATE&quot;*****<br><br>AH! At last, I am free of classes! My teachers shake their head and laugh as I run out the door!<br>I am a good student of Magic..This they know, but am also a Wildly Free Spirit and at times &quot;TOO CURIOUS&quot; for mine own good...Which later I will learn to Regret!!<br><br>As I enter into the courtyard in Qeynos, I stretch--Free of the bounds of Science--and breathe in the Pure Warm Air of the Valley. I am happy and carefree today! No more school for the season. I think to myself....It is NOW time for my first Adventure!<br><br>I summon my pet. - &quot;Anthros&quot;...Appears by my side, weilding his short sword and shield so gallantly for one so young!<br>He is as excited as I by what we are about to do today!<br>&quot;Anthros&quot; nudges me playfully, ready to begin our outing.<br><br>&quot;Wait&quot;, I tell him, &quot;I have to do something first.&quot; I laugh to myself as I run quickly inside to get provisions for myself and my pet. Once more outside, I see &quot;Anthros&quot; frowning at me for being so forgetful. I give him a warm hug and All is forgiven by him!<br><br>We start out following the path, but up ahead, I see too many distractions in the distance. I point out to &quot;Anthros&quot; a beautiful Violet flower that is rare to this land and know it calls to me. I know I shouldn't leave the path, but temptation to smell and look upon it's beauty consumes me.<br><br>This leads us farther and farther into the lands I have come to love so deeply and DO NOT pay attention to where we have traveled and the lateness of the hour.<br><br>&quot;Anthros&quot; starts to become very agitated by my side!!<br>I look to him and he points his sword to the ridge South of us. Darkening Heavens surround the valley! &quot;OH MY GOODNESS!!!!&quot; Black, angry clouds are racing towards us! I smell the heavy rain in the air!!!<br>Something even MORE terrifying has occured to me!! I know not where we are!! For a moment, Fear rushes through me, but with my teachings, I have learned to become calm and to reason.<br><br>&quot;ANTHROS&quot; is having NONE of This!!!! He is sensing great danger all around us!!<br>He tries to nudge me to a safe place, but alas....tisss TOO LATE!!<br><br>The heavy clouds above open...Spilling their torrent upon us! Lightening streaks across the skies....Thunder so loud it makes mine head ache!!!<br>Immediately, I am soaked and shivering with-in my pale silk gown.<br><br>An evil wind begins to howl down the canyon towards us, bringing this message....&quot;Mystiina&quot;.....&quot;Myssstiina&quot;...&quot;My Fair One&quot;. &quot;Evil comes to you and your beloved pet this day.&quot; &quot;Prepare Yourselves to DIE!!&quot;<br><br>By now, &quot;Anthros&quot; is beside himself!! His panic has now cut clean to my soul!!! I realize now my free spirit and youth may get up both killed!<br><br>In the distance, I hear a sound. I turn to it. There, before me is a Blackness that is NOT Human, or even of this plane! It is moving quickly and with a purpose, that I know NOW, will probably seal our DOOM!<br><br>I reach to the Velvet Blackened Sky and cry out to my goddess to help me.....She does NOT hear my cries!!! We are Alone!!!!!<br><br>Lightening strikes across the heavens and lights up a horror I know NO bounds to describe. - It is a large black pulsing mist of pure hate, and it is headed for my beloved pet &quot;Anthros!!!!&quot;<br>&quot;NOOO&quot;! I cry out, &quot;Take Me Instead&quot;!!<br>In my terrified mind I hear, &quot;In time my Lil One&quot;....&quot;In Time&quot;.<br><br>I race to intercept this black horror that has engulfed my beloved pet, but it is toooo late!<br>&quot;Anthros&quot; screams out his pain and pleads with me to RUN!!!<br>I am helpless against this Nightmare I have created and can not move! As I watch &quot;Anthros&quot; fight his last fight..I sense another. It is his mate, and she is coming for ME!!!<br>It rasps, saying &quot;Ah&quot;..&quot;An Enchantresssss&quot;. &quot;Our kind have been watching and waiting for such a moment as this&quot;!!<br><br>I release spell after deadly spell onto her, but she flicks them away as if they were nothing to her!<br>This She-Devil CAN NOT be brought DOWN!! Advancing slowly, she circles me. I am being drawn closer and closer to that evil mist!! Helpless now, she strikes! Going down on one knee, I feel my very life essence ebbing away...Being consumed by this Spawn from Hell's Gate.<br>I fight the pain, but know that this first battle of my youth will NOT be won by me.<br><br>As I lay broken and bleeding upon this rocky plain, I give one last whisper to this Demon Mist. &quot;Know This&quot; - My brothers and sisters will Avenge Me!!&quot; I am young and will be forgiven for my faults.&quot; &quot;Your kind will be hunted endlessly until you are wiped off this plane for all time!!&quot;<br><br>Slowly, As I pass from here, a lesson has been learned by me. Unfortunately, &quot;TOO LATE.&quot;<br><br>Until the time has come in your seasons to be more knowledgeable and stronger, both in Spirit and Body...&quot;Guards Oneself Against Curiousity!!&quot; &quot;Stay On the Paths!!&quot;<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br>Azzarria - "Stormchild"<br>"The Huntress"</td></tr>
