	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=189461><span id=Sage>Taimarawee</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>20 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>**A Hardened Figher...Yet, gentle soul has come into my life.<br><br>We met long ago when I was but a Child. He..close friends to my Father's Shaman &quot;Drinel&quot;. Frequently making visits to our small village of Halas. When their meetings ended he and &quot;Drinel&quot; would come to our evening fires and join in the telling of tales.<br>Ever watching me with those intense Green Eyes!...Thinking naught of this in my youth, I bore it no further heed.<br><br>**&quot;Till Now&quot;!!**<br><br>Once Again we meet!<br>&quot;I&quot; .. fighting a losing battle with a Sand Giant named &quot;Lorr&quot;!!<br>Little did I know, that the brother to this giant**&quot;Gorr&quot;, would possibly be my undoing on this plane!!<br><br>Assisting me in this violent battle of brawn versus skill...it quickly became know to me, how deadly this Ranger really was!<br>Arrow after Arrow reaching its mark on &quot;Lorr&quot;...the giant wavered.<br><br>I stepped in to finish the kill, when &quot;Lorr&quot;, with surprising speed unknown to one of his kind...Bashed me!!<br>Reeling, I tried to step back, but the damage had already been done!! Quickly the Ranger threw me to one side!! With deadly skill and aim his Arrow flew, striking between the eyes of &quot;Lorr&quot;!<br>The air..Sickening with the smell of death, he toppled! Leaving me his words of doom...&quot;My Brother&quot;...&quot;Will be your undoing, Beastlord&quot;!!!<br><br>Badly hurt, yet still standing, I turn to thank this man...BUT he has gone! What manner of Magic is this!! No man may disappear thus!!!<br><br>Shouting Out to the Winds...I offer my help and thanks to him. In return, my ears hear his message.<br>&quot;Nay M'Lady&quot;...&quot;Only Yer Heart Do I require&quot;.<br><br>I know he follows me - I feel his presence at every turn. Yet, when I see him in the distance and approach..He is gone once more! Blending with the area as if he were ONE with it!<br><br>Why was I chosen by he? Me..A Barbarian Beastlord..Wild and Untamed! My life is &quot;War &amp; Death&quot;!! Destruction coursing thru me to defeat evil vile creatures of Norrath!<br><br>&quot;NO MAN&quot; has held me heart, other than my Father!!<br><br>Shaking my head, I go on. I soon realize the toll this battle has put upon me. Weak and vunerable, with a fever rising...I sense creatures that know this!<br>Now...it seems, &quot;I&quot; am Their &quot;Prey&quot;!! Constantly hunting and stalking me - Never leaving me to rest....!<br><br>Blindly going forward, knowing I have to leave this dangerous area - I find food, shelter and herbs available to me.<br>How does he know my path? Why does he care? WHO is this Ranger?? What glimpses I see of him - I see only concern and protection in those beautiful green eyes.<br><br>My head is fevered...questions aside, I take solence in what he has offered. <br><br>At peace for the moment beside my small fire, with Ponpi' nestled close to me...My thoughts drift once more to him.<br><br>Tired &amp; matured beyond my years of this constant fighting - I feel the beginnings of feelings unknown to me .. Starting to thread thru my Soul. Gentle waves of feelings.. Like my Beloved Lake, soothing me. - With these thoughts and feelings I snuggle closer to my pet and watch the night sky unfold before me.<br><br>Dawn approaches and sleep still not finding me, I rise.<br>Stiff and sore, with fever flowing through me - I stir the embers of my small fire coaxing it back to life, making a small quick meal for myself and Ponpi'.<br><br>Gathering my provisions and getting ready to embark once more - I sense something on the winds!!!! Why is not Ponpi' alerted to this!!!<br><br>Not clearly thinking - I close my eyes and a BloodLust rises within me I can not stop!!! &quot;Nay&quot;!! I am tired - I will NOT Die here in this godforsaken barren sand!! Not Yet!!<br>Bringing my deadly Ulaks out, I turn and cutting down, I draw a gastly slice across...........The chest of my protector!!!! &quot;Nay&quot;!!! &quot;My Gods&quot;!! &quot;What have I done&quot;??!!<br><br>Blood runs down his armor, staining those vibrant colors of Silver and Green to a dull Crimson Red!!!<br><br>**TIME SLOWS.........! Thru my tears, I see him reach for me as the ground slowly rises up and pulls me to it's Sandy Softness!<br><br>**&quot;Gods&quot;! &quot;I am too warm&quot;!<br><br>Throwing off a soft blanket of material that feels strange to me, I try to rise.<br>My heads swims - I lay back down once more. <br>Confusion sets in to my addled thoughts....&quot;Where am I&quot;?? Thru a mist of fevered pain, I see My Ranger bending over me. <br>With gentle cool strokes of his fingers, pushing back my auburn hair, he rests his hand on my fevered brow......&quot;I Calm&quot;.<br><br>As he slowly bends forward - I smell leather and the cool sharp scent of forest upon him. Bending closer still...his warm breathe upon my ear, I hear his words...Deep, strong, reaching into my very soul!!<br><br>&quot;StormChild&quot; - hear me now! &quot;You are safe, in my homeland of &quot;The Glades&quot;.<br>&quot;Rest, my wild beauty&quot; - &quot;for when you next awake, my heart needs to tell you a tale of &quot;US&quot;.<br><br>A smile plays across my lips as I slowly ease - once more - into a Velvet Darkness of Peace and Possibly a new found love!<br><br>Part Four..to be continued****<br></p>&nbsp;<br>Azzarria - "Stormchild"<br>"The Huntress"</td></tr>
